8 An Act relating to professions and occupations;
amending Section 3, Chapter 291, O.S.L. 2024 (59 O.S.
9 Supp. 2024, Section 538.3), which relates to laser
hair removal practitioners; authorizing certain
10 professionals to perform laser hair removal;
requiring oversight of laser hair removal facilities
11 by certain professionals; requiring the establishment
of patient relationships; providing for the creation
12 of patient charts; deleting evaluation or referral
exception; and declaring an emergency.
