15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 3, Chapter 291, O.S.L.
17 2024 (59 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 538.3), is amended to read as
18 follows:
19 Section 538.3. A. A laser practitioner shall only perform
20 laser hair removal using lasers or pulsed light devices approved by
21 the United States Food and Drug Administration (FDA) for noninvasive
22 procedures.
23 B. A person shall not perform or attempt to perform laser hair
24 removal unless the person holds the appropriate health professional
