8 Every physician or physician assistant or Advanced Practice
9 Registered Nurse shall establish a relationship with patients which
10 shall include an initial evaluation, prior to treatment, that is
11 either face-to-face or via telemedicine that is performed by the
12 physician or physician assistant or Advanced Practice Registered
13 Nurse.
14 As part of the patient relationship, each physician or certified
15 physician assistant or certified Advanced Practice Registered Nurse
16 shall create a patient chart. The chart shall contain an informed
17 consent, a treatment plan that includes risks, benefits,
18 alternatives, follow-up, and care for potential complications.
19 E. A physician shall not be required to be physically present
20 or to supervise laser hair removal, but shall be available for
21 communication during the procedure, either in person or by two-way,
22 real time interactive communication.
